name: Covid 19 Lab Tests
query:
SELECT
    'Initial' as "Type of Test:Data:150",
  `tabLab Test`.name as "Sample Number:Link/Lab Test:200",
   `tabLab Test`.template as "Assay Kit Name:Data:300",
  `tabLab Test`.patient_name as "Client Name(First, Middle, Last):Data:200",
  `tabLab Test`.patient_age as "Age:Data:200",
    'Years' as "Age Unit:Data:100",
  `tabLab Test`.identification_number as "Identification Number:Data:200",
  
  `tabLab Test`.creation as "Date of sample collection (DD/MM/YYYY):Date:220",
  `tabLab Test`.mobile as "Telephone Number:Data:120",
  `tabLab Test`.county as "County of Residence:Link/County:200",
  `tabLab Test`.sub_county as "Sub-County of Residence:Link/Sub County:200",
  `tabLab Test`.physical_address as "Village/Estate of Residence:Link/Sub County:200",
  `tabNormal Test Result`.result_value  as "Test Result:Data:200"
  
FROM
  `tabLab Test`,`tabNormal Test Result` WHERE `tabLab Test`.name = `tabNormal Test Result`.parent
